contentrichtext.text: '''Isan''', or '''ISAN''', may refer to: * [[Isan]], a region of Thailand ** [[Isan people]] ** [[Isan language]], the collective name for the dialects of the Lao language as they are spoken in Thailand * '''Isan''', a dialect of the Yupna branch of the [[Finisterre languages|Finisterre language family]] * [[International Standard Audiovisual Number]], an ISO Standard for identification of audiovisual works. * [[Isan (band)]], a British electronic music group * [[Institute for Spectroscopy Russian Academy of Sciences]] {{disambig}}
